title: VA Indie Folk Pop September 2013 - Confusion (Dutch Treat I2 HQ)
description:
The eighth and for last Indie Playlist of September 2013 has become quite special. Lovely and spicy at the same time. Hopeful music for dreamers.. and all others.... Enjoy,

In retrospect, I would like to dedicate this playlist to the creator of the Painting from Tamra Pfeifle Davisson on the cover. The picture struck me while searching for Confusion, as seeing a lot of truth suddenly. Something to think (and listen) about.
